    "Top salient genes identified by XGDP when predicting drug responses for Dasatinib, Erlotinib and Ponatinib.",
    "This study introduced a novel framework XGDP to predict response levels of anti-cancer drugs and discover underlying mechanism of action of drugs.",
    "To enhance the predictive power of GNN models, first we adapted the Morgan algorithm that is used for computing ECFPs to form our node features.",
    "Same procedures as Morgan algorithm were followed to identify the substructures of the molecule but the feature vector of each atom was assigned as the membership of the identified structures.",
